  * Rebuild for dependencies

 -- Constantin Piber <cp.piber@gmail.com>  Wed, 18 Feb 2026 20:29:24 +0100

hyprland (0.53.3-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.53.3
  * dd220efe version: bump to 0.53.3
  * bf665d05 hyprpm: fix build step execution
  * ec060999 hyprctl: remove trailing comma from json object (#13042)

 -- Constantin Piber <cp.piber@gmail.com>  Sat, 24 Jan 2026 21:36:17 +0100

hyprland (0.53.2-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.53.2
  * 39f3fedd [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * c86e56ed version: bump to 0.53.2
  * df8a24c0 hyprpm: use provided pkgconf env if available
  * a213321a desktop: restore invisible floating window alpha/opacity
    when focused over fullscreen (#12994)
  * 7e85c629 animation: reset tick state on session activation (#13024)
  * 34610223 hyprerror: clear reserved area on destroy (#13046)
  * 4350f47a Nix: re-enable hyprpm
  * 486019e5 hyprpm: drop meson dep
  * e266f8bf hyprpm,Makefile: drop cmake ninja build
  * 65a70936 anr: remove window on closewindow (#13007)
  * 64818bd1 desktop/ruleApplicator: fix typo in border color rule
    parsing (#12995)
  * 6b7fd1da desktop/window: avoid uaf on instant removal of a window
  * 6eb6aeb7 desktop/workspaceHistory: fix tracking for multiple
    monitors (#12979)
  * 39029454 desktop/window: track explicit workspace assignments to
    prevent X11 configure overwrites (#12850)
  * 4ac5fc17 fix: handle fullscreen windows on special workspaces
    (#12851)
  * 7bc7a7af animationMgr: avoid uaf in ::tick() if handleUpdate
    destroys AV
  * 68743492 desktop/reservedArea: clamp dynamic types to 0
  * 380c63f8 desktop/reservedArea: clamp to 0
  * 50ce5504 config: don't crash on permission with a config check
  * f2a42a77 start: use nixGL if Hyprland is nix but not NixOS (#12845)
  * 7c9fb6e8 start: add parent-death handling for BSDs (#12863)
  * 49293f03 config: return windowrulev2 layerrulev2 error messages
    (#12847)
  * e11dbc05 testers: add missing #include <unistd.h> (#12862)
  * 9a1311e3 pluginsystem: fix crash when unloading plugin hyprctl
    commands (#12821)

 -- Constantin Piber <cp.piber@gmail.com>  Fri, 23 Jan 2026 22:05:22 +0100

hyprland (0.53.1-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.53.1
  * ab1d80f3 version: bump to 0.53.1
  * 3254fa7b desktop/layerRuleApplicator: fix an epic c+p fail
  * 27bee5bf core/xwaylandmgr: fix min/max clamp potentially crashing
  * 23d8c372 dekstop/window: read static rules before guessing initial
    size if possible (#12783)
  * c57b20dc desktop/window: use workArea for idealBB (#12802)
  * 429e366a input/ti: avoid sending events to inactive TIs
  * 2ca2c1c7 desktop/LS: avoid creating an invalid LS if no monitor
    could be found (#12787)
  * 587402e5 input: guard null `view()` when processing mouse down
    (#12772)
  * 12d68196 desktop/window: go back to the previously focused window in
    a group (#12763)
  * 127e206e desktopAnimationMgr: fix slide direction

 -- Constantin Piber <cp.piber@gmail.com>  Sat, 03 Jan 2026 08:36:17 +0100

hyprland (0.53.0-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.53.0
  * ea444c35 version: bump to 0.53.0
  * 6a055fc7 cm: allow force disabling WCG and HDR per monitor (#12733)
  * a8452705 gitignore: add hyprland.desktop generated by cmake
  * e5d20b56 keybinds: simulate mouse movement after bringing active
    window to top (#12703)
  * 5faa66d2 protocols/cm: fix CColorManagementSurface
    m_imageDescription init (#12734)
  * 610c59dc opengl: properly combine transforms in renderTexture
  * e5f22c06 master: fix placement with center_ignores_reserved (#12695)
  * 6d3b17ee render/cm: various updates, remove old protocols (#12693)
  * 42447a50 rules/windowRuleApplicator: fix min/max size effects
    (#12491)
  * d7f26038 keybinds: fix multikey binds breaking after scroll wheel
    events (#12638)
  * 33df518f input: fix pending perm keyboards being enabled
  * 9ea56505 example/hyprland.desktop: fix path
  * 1f1a39d4 example/hyprland.desktop: install with full path in Exec
  * 14c49230 Nix: re-enable uwsm desktop file
  * 25250527 start: avoid crash in dtor after forceQuit
  * f7f357f1 keybindmgr: fix focusCurrentOrLast
  * abffe750 desktop/window: improve fullscreen handling for grouped
    windows
  * 60efbf3f desktop/ls: only update the ls in question for commit to
    change layer
  * 712bcfbc protocols/xdg-shell: fix crash on null parent in pin
    (#12694)
  * c87a1a76 i18n: add Danish translation (#12333)
  * 7bd20737 window: automatically pin child windows (#12224)
  * b9bef695 Desktop/history: Move history to desktop (#12676)
  * 70f54a1e animationmgr: avoid possible uaf in handling anim updates
  * f6c5c659 i18n: Add Arabic translations for safemode (#12670)
  * c23a0c20 [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * 3bbbb5aa core: add missing headers (#12686)
  * 315806f5 tablet: added option to hide cursor (#12525)
  * 6175ecd4 debug: move to hyprutils' logger (#12673)
  * f88deb92 compositor: warn on start via a log about start-hyprland
  * 18901b8e desktop/windowRule: force center and move rules to override
    each other (#12618)
  * 70985584 desktop/layer: store aboveFs property and use that
  * 59438908 i18n: more natural Japanese translation (#12649)
  * cbfdbe9f desktop/popup: fix invalid surface coord
  * c94a9817 input: simplify mouseMoveUnified a tad
  * beb1b578 input: cleanup sendMotionEventsToFocused()
  * c5beecb2 desktop/popup: minor improvements
  * 6e09eb2e desktop/windowRules: fix disabling binary window rules with
    override (#12635)
  * 6b491e4d core/compositor: remove a monitor reset on cleanup (#12645)
  * 4036c37e hyprctl: add nix flag (#12653)
  * 7ccc57eb animation: migrate PHLANIMVAR from SP to UP (#12486)
  * e4a8f2b1 renderer: add zoom with detached camera (#12548)
  * 6535ff07 anr: don't create for anr dialogs (#12601)
  * 05ccbb2f hyprpm: added plugin author (#12594)
  * 09e195d1 compositor: fix isPointOnReservedArea
  * fd5e790d compositor: return nullptr when cursor is outside of a
    maximized windows' box
  * 69db0bca compositor: early return on no monitor (#12637)
  * 8dfdcfb3 compositor: dont try to focus unmapped window (#12629)
  * 57007365 cm: handle CM for SDR content with cm=hdr, cm_sdr_eotf=2
    (#12127)
  * 75f6435f window: only damage floating on clamped size change
    (#12633)
  * 5dd22480 desktop/view: use aliveAndVisible for most things (#12631)
  * 2ca7ad7e ci: disable comments for members
  * 9aa31340 protocols/datadevice: avoid double leave
  * 1ff801f5 Nix: fix glaze build for CI and devShell (#12616)
  * 3cf6dfd7 opengl: default initialize m_capStatus (#12619)
  * f58c80fd monitor: remove monitor from list on disconnect before
    unsafestate (#12544)
