hyprland (0.52.0-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.52.0
  * f56ec180 version: bump to 0.52.0
  * fd50e78b render/cm: change non_shader_cm ignore behavior and set
    default to it (#12210)
  * 06198120 core: qtutils -> guiutils (#12231)
  * 3fc8cb82 cm: follow preferred srgb eotf for screencopy (#12230)
  * 1ca6058b chore: fix non-relative imports (#12228)
  * ca4b68e4 renderer: fix fractional scale artifact (#12219)
  * 8e8bfbb0 protocols: add Fifo-v1 and commit-timing-v1 (#12052)
  * c757fd37 compositor: block parent window interaction when modal
    dialog children window is open (#12057)
  * 46b71eda [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * d82538c6 protocols/dmabuf: handle null pointer in
    CLinuxDMABufV1Protocol::resetFormatTable (#12207)
  * 8e9add2a sessionlock: fix crash when sendScale is called on a
    disconnected (#12171)
  * 5e6cec96 cursor: refactor override handling (#12166)
  * 6ade4d58 layout: fit floating window on toggle to float (#12139)
  * 83a0a620 protocols/core: round dnd drop surface box
  * ff50dc36 renderer/cm: allow gamma 2.2 instead of sRGB EOTF (#12094)
  * ce9787b3 xwayland: set _NET_WORKAREA property (#12148)
  * 9eb82774 Nix: build hyprtester along with hyprland
  * a2f48ea4 CMake: allow building hyprtester without running tests
  * 309c3c78 Nix/tests: wl-copy -> wl-clipboard
  * 0907fdf4 CI/release: run cmake configure
  * 431325ff config/rule: don't populate ID field for automatically id-
    managed workspaces
  * 40831a90 Nix/tests: add wl-copy
  * b186d3bf pass/surface: check for LS size anim for misaligned
    fractional
  * 560c53d8 monitor/dpms: fix possible invalid state
  * fd42e9d0 CI/release: remove generateVersion call
  * 17d0d696 screencopy: wait longer to re-enable DS (#12135)
  * 88e34d7d IME: do not share keys/mods states from grabbed keyboards
    with ime keys/mods (#11917)
  * 05aa4e1c compositor: check for monitor layout issues post rule apply
  * 748d2f65 xdg-shell: implement invalid parent errors
  * 6ea4769b EGL: minor egl changes (#12132)
  * 72cbb790 layer-shell: fix fullscreen alpha when changing layers
    (#12124)
  * b6f94699 meson: disable lto (#12129)
  * b10b9660 screencopy: fix missing XBGR2101010 format with
    screencopy_force_8b (#12125)
  * da04afa4 surface: fix xwayland zero scaling damage calcs (#12123)
  * 34812c33 hyprctl: include color management presets and sdr
    information (#12019)
  * 117e38db cmake: fix git lookup for when building out of
    srcdir(#12116)
  * 151b5f69 dwindle: rework split logic to be fully gap-aware (#12047)
  * aa5a239a [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * 019589e2 build: replace generateVersion.sh (#12110)
  * 057695bc desktopAnimationMgr: don't set fade 0 for members of a fs
    group (#12091)
  * 892f642f plugins: incorporate hyprdep ABI into plugin info (#12001)
  * d560c264 internal: fix cf
  * 02b0c563 xwm: attempt to guess mime in sendData for DnD
  * 4926332c monitor: remove spammy trace log
  * 46dab01b renderer: add more uniforms to the screen shader (#11986)
  * 474cd004 [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * a4200acf input: fix refocus on grab dismiss (#12014)
  * 59ff7b2f dispatchers: add forceidle (#11922)
  * ba077d8f renderer: clean up surface UV size calcs, fix issues
    (#12070)
  * 39d62e14 protocols: fix output power protocol not sending mode
    confirmation (#12072)
  * 6607c644 renderer: add 1fv and 2fv uniform support (#12080)
  * f3e13193 timer: constify methods (#12079)
  * 8164b90b config: fix crash when some configurations include non-
    integer values (#12056)
  * 36c0477d tests: disable shortcut test for ci
  * ab11af96 ext-foreign-toplevel: remove stale entries when remapping
    (#12037)
  * e40873be renderer: add cursor:zoom_disable_aa for controlling AA on
    zoom (#12025)
  * 60529e81 renderer: round box in damageBox
  * f324a3a5 functionHook: fix distance check
  * ee5d05f0 hookSystem: fix anchor point for mmap
  * bbb83317 Nix: drop ninja for CMake build
  * 0d6d19b2 Revert "nix: use meson"
  * 541ef60f CMake: print pch messages based on var
  * 4b55ec68 windowrules: add modal prop (#12024)
  * 7fcaf332 layouts: apply [min|max]size window rules to dwindle &
    master layouts (#11898)
  * 6582f42d meson: disable lto explicitly
  * ed936430 core: disable lto for hyprland builds (#11972)
  * d599513d config: add automatic closing to submaps (#11760)
  * 6a01c399 input: add option to rotate device input (#11947)
  * da31e82a internal: prevent early exit processes from being zombies
    (#11995)
  * 32f32333 dmabuffer: ensure we only create one texture per buffer
    (#11990)
  * 2b0926dc tests: disable one test as it fails on ci
  * b965fb2a flake.lock: bump hyprutils
  * 82759d40 buffer: move texture creation to commit time (#11964)
  * 0dc45b54 managers/helpers: add missing includes (#11969)
  * ba24547d dispatchers: add set, unset and toggle to fullscreen
    (#11893)
  * 5ba2d221 compositor: make wl_surface::frame follow pending states
    (#11953)
  * 5a208621 hookSystem: use a full trampo setup for hooks
  * c3747fab hookSystem: fix anchoring in seekNewPageAddr()
  * dc72259a core/compositor: revert make wl_surface::frame follow
    pending states (#11896)
  * 02cda6be systeminfo: log system package versions (#11946)
  * 73f06434 keybinds: fix repeat and long press keybinds release
    (#11863)
  * 17e77e04 core/compositor: make wl_surface::frame follow pending
    states (#11896)
  * cfac2725 debug: fix data race in Debug::log() (#11931)
  * 76d99874 cm: handle inert cm outputs (#11916)
  * b7ef892e [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * f0b4164e cm: fix primaries to proto scale (#11914)
  * 3bcfa94e renderer: add render:non_shader_cm and fixes (#11900)
  * c467bb26 renderer: fix popup fadeout blur (#11756)
  * e0c96276 renderer: optimize border drawcalls (#11891)
  * 378438ff config: increase default anr_missed_pings value
  * 13648d19 protocols/seat: force down rounding of coords at the
    surface edge (#11890)
  * 8c54c9b4 protocols/cm: remove unneeded preferred ref (#11877)
  * 38c1e72c rules: fix some monitor rules (#11873)
  * 09596725 renderer/cm: add more monitor cm options (#11861)
  * 4d82cc59 internal: fix clang-tidy "errors" (#11862)
  * 43fb4753 gestures: fix gesture direction detection (#11852)
  * f854b5bf deco: reduce virtual calls in drop shadow
  * eb25dfd3 opengl: move from unordered_set to array
  * b6278857 decoration: reduce virtual calls
  * c30036bd CI/Arch: build hyprgraphics after hyprutils
  * 766acadc seat: release depressed modifiers on leave (#11854)
  * ef479ff5 viewporter: clamp sub-pixel overflow (#11845)
  * 6f1d2e77 config: fix rules with no parameters not being counted as
    invalid (#11849)
  * ae445606 config: allow negative to be used with tags. (#11779)
  * 4f3dd1dd config: fix gesture dispatcher parsing with whitespaces
    (#11784)
  * d8f61575 config: support more than 1 window rule per rule line.
    (#11689)
  * 7ce451d2 renderer: disable anti-aliasing on cursor:zoom_factor
    (#6135) (#11828)
  * 5212099b layout: avoid nullptr deref (#11831)
  * 8cce3b98 shm: refactor to UP and correct m_data check (#11820)
  * 683fc77f hyprctl: nullptr guard --systeminfo (#11822)
  * ec9a72d9 workspaces: fix persistence with no monitor specified
    (#11807)
  * 31bd9ec4 foreign-toplevel: continue past skipped invalid windows
    (#11804)
  * 29b103c3 exec: Spawn processes as direct children (#11735)
  * 70a7047e renderer: fix uv scaling detection (#11789)
  * 26f29352 renderer: add "noscreenshare" layer rule (#11664)
  * 45f007d4 ci: remove duplicate cp and redundant mkdir commands
  * 22c8bc9b CI/Nix: Allow running CI in forks
  * 26cbc673 renderer: fix uv calculations once and for all (#11770)
  * 41dad381 config: fix multi-argument gesture dispatcher parsing
    (#11721)
  * 83843908 vkeyboard: update cached mods before IME; add share_states
    = 2 config option (#11720)
  * 6a88f2e8 monitors: auto apply suggested scale and notify the user.
    (#11753)
  * 88326075 [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * 8fc7b2c1 input: fix virtual keyboard keymaps (#11763)
  * afd1e717 renderer: fix inconsistent border thickness for
    roundingPower < 2 (#11752)
  * 4fc95d64 renderer: asynchronously load background tex (#11749)
  * 91f592a8 workspace: fix relative workspaces with monitor descs
  * 059ec60e hyprpm: make temp root if not present
  * 56480779 animation: fix slide/slidefade to accept forced direction
    (#11725)
  * 1cb8cd39 solitary: fix check for config error (#11733)
  * 7fd6998f core: fix clang-format
  * 5e96fac5 presentation: fix vrr check for reporting no refresh time
  * 4a9c4dbc gestures/fs: fix typo
  * 9e74d0ae renderer: clamp blur:passes 1-8
  * 559024c3 gestures/float: fix typo
  * 16c18dde windows: fix no decorate not disabling borders (#11673)
  * adbf7c86 input: handle tablet active area scaling when axes swap due
    to rotation (#11661)
  * 797bfe90 dispatchers: fix movecursor not updating client pos
    (#11672)
  * 38169c8f input: support xkb v2 format (#11482)
  * c7b99691 render/OpenGL: fix compilation for 32bit systems (#11667)
  * 231b8007 flake.lock: update
  * 8a959b43 meson: set minimum version

