hyprland (0.50.0-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.50.0
  * c4a4c341 version: bump to 0.50.0
  * d4fbedcd core: never use hw cursors when tearing
  * 5bfe6dc7 config: disable hw on mgpu nvidia by default (#11018)
  * 8453fbf4 snap: fix `border_overlap` option for monitor snapping
    (#10987)
  * e15014e0 protocols/cm: Fix preferred image description (#11026)
  * bc764f70 protocols: Remove incorrect CM proto debug check and fix
    preferred image description (#11023)
  * 06fcdbd9 renderer: use makeUnique for session-lock render passes
    (#11019)
  * 01971cb6 session-lock: don't render workspaces when locked (#10865)
  * d0f58baf screencopy: ignore hidden windows in noscreenshare
  * 8bfff878 debugOverlay: fix tick measurement
  * 6821723b splashes: add zacoons' splash
  * e589adb0 config: remove render_ahead* config options
  * 523eed04 xwl: dont mark the even source as readable
  * e6bb8096 monintor: remove rathandler
  * b5433bb7 singlepixel: move to unique ptrs
  * bcb96c55 presentation: move to unique ptrs
  * f22b5971 dmabuf: move to unique ptrs
  * 87653077 cursorshape: use unique ptrs
  * a21882be ctmcontrol: move to unique ptrs
  * 37be9a89 alphamodifier: move to unique ptrs
  * f5af40af renderpass: use unique ptr instead of shared ptr
  * 6375e471 config: disable new_render_scheduling by default
  * c6497a71 internal: Prevent double-free in attemptDirectScanout
    (#10974)
