  * bb958a9e pass: overload TexPass constructor
  * c75f8509 renderer: move render calculation behind if case
  * 4a30e2ac eventloop: RAII the even source on readable fd
  * ceec1943 compositor: dont send around int max values
  * 83c453cb plugins: made currentWindow available in RENDER_PRE_WINDOW
    (#10957)
  * 54369adf internal: iso C++ prohibits anonymous structs (#10955)
