  * aea81320 buffer: don't use crazy listener::emit()
  * cf7e3aa4 renderer/cm: Add automatic hdr (#9785)
  * c7c8ca47 config: add missing description for enforce_permissions
  * 24e5f997 hyprctl: print no open windows instead of invalid request
    on empty clients
