  * 4be32dbf xwayland: Don't leave shell process (#10802)
  * 8ebff194 [gha] build man pages
  * a301d54d treewide: hyprland.org -> hypr.land
  * ff2f8564 CI/Nix: add cache-nix-action
  * b49d0ca2 xwayland: Fix crash when copying from wayland to xwayland
    (#10786)
  * 86b5e3bf config: nuke explicit_sync settings
  * 54ccf9c6 renderer: make lock fail textures dynamically loaded
  * e999ad66 hookSystem: avoid using manual mem management, fix leak
  * 9fb6b5d9 input: Fix incorrect localcoords with a surface above an
    XWayland window (#10773)
  * 0fb63c68 permissions: properly print config requests for plugins
  * 83a4c610 plugins: don't update config plugins on state unchanged
  * bef1321f xwayland: fix minor errors in previous refactor (#10763)
  * 0ece4af3 grpupbar: Add config options to color inactive and locked
    groupbar titles (#10667)
  * aba2cfe7 asyncDialogBox: lock box in fdWrite to prevent a uaf
    (#10759)
  * d4e8a440 windowrules/move: clamp max pos in onscreen to avoid assert
    crash
  * 1905c41c xwayland: Use RAII instead or freeing memory manually
    (#10677)
  * bd5703d5 protocols/cm: fix wp invalid luminance check (#10752)
  * d037c542 protocols: support xdg-shell v7
  * c3894d92 config/monitor: Add monitor v2 HDR rules (#10623)
  * 3db3baa1 opengl: use a stack for storing monitor transform enabled
  * 57d20a1b internal: clean up dead snapshot code
  * 472b52bc cursor: reset hc data after theme change
  * 79b9edb8 [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * f08167c8 input: add sticky option for drag_lock (#10702)
  * ad854062 drm-lease: Add Multi-GPU Support (#10099)
  * d14f81e6 protocols: whitelist wp_color_manager_v1 for
    security_context (#10723)
  * 826061d1 README: Update image cdn (#10722)
  * 748419fa hyprpm: check version and update automatically on add
    (#10706)
  * 412c7dc7 renderer: fixup some missing fadeout cases with special
  * 8329de1a input: grab the correct active workspace on mouseMove
  * 144885d8 anr: make dialog disappear if the app dies
  * f7526d6b renderer: refuse rendering invalid resolutions
  * 6910ca76 protocols/subcompositor: fixup place_above and _below
  * 6bdb1f41 dwindle: add the ability to specify an aspect ratio for a
    singular window (#10650)
  * 81468253 hyprpm: fix typo in help message (#10687)
  * 231e01e3 hyprctl: don't detect a negative value as a parameter
    (#10671)
  * c6f713fe screencopy: fix incorrect noscreenshare positions with
    monitor scaling (#10674)
  * 91967f8e renderer: fix incorrect cursor position when screencopy
    region with monitor scaling (#10675)
  * 0a47575c internal: Use `using` instead of `#define` to alias smart
    pointers (#10673)
  * 88017709 [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * 66b99bd2 monitor: ensure autoDir is applied when changed (#10672)
  * 2794f485 hyprctl: Remove exceptions, use modern error handling
    (#10664)
  * 0ac3bef7 input: support configuring drag_3fg from libinput (#10631)
  * 456c820d assets: update header
  * c35c2fea config: Restore auto-center-* for monitors (#10660)
  * d6fbd893 nix: use gcc15-built dependencies
  * fb7548cb screencopy: fix applying `noscreenshare` to invisible
    special workspaces (#10628)
  * 423b69f5 config: add group: selector (#10588)
  * abdfc5ea config: add a new monitor v2 config syntax (#9761)
  * 59c886d8 internal: Catch filesystem exceptions while iterating
    RunTimeDir (#10648)
  * d7a87ce6 xwayland: fix xwayland -> wayland clipboard (#10646)
  * d9f7448d xwayland: pad pid with leading zeroes in lockfile
  * b5c0d0b8 keybinds: add an option to respect gaps out for floating to
    movewindow (#9360)
  * b1d0a727 internal: Center window on parent if available (#10582)
  * ef2c73af internal: embed example config (#10608)
  * 16c62a6d internal: Fix HyprError not displaying at startup (#10606)
  * 2d1c6f88 xwm: Refactored functions in XWM.cpp (#10569)
  * 82b85495 hyprpm: refuse adding a new repo without update
  * 69c2b292 internal: refactor to use empty() (#10599)
  * 4078e1d1 refactor: replace all `typedef` with `using` (#10594)
  * af2fdb5d nix: use gcc15
  * 9190443d refactor: use std::ranges whenever possible (#10584)
  * 9bf1b491 snap: add option to respect gaps (#10524)
  * 5cc6cb49 groupbar: force recalc on visibility changes
  * 9b327ddf monitor: mark 0, 0 presentation timestamps as invalid
  * 24915a3a windowrules: Add noscreenshare (#10482)
  * 90d0b8ec core: add auto-center arrangements (#10527)
  * ddb9f839 config: fix inconsistant hint of default value (#10556)
  * a62ccb16 config: fix crash on misnamed variable (#10549)
  * be6ee6e5 cmake: disable gprof by default
  * c2805aad config: add maxwidth monitor resolution mode (#10528)
  * 4c4c9bb3 dwindle: add better automatic window drag and drop
    direction detection (#9704)
  * 292a7456 eventLoop: fixup headers
  * 23470502 pass/surface: make sure popup blurs are marked for require
    live blur
  * a58ab20e debug/pass: show live/precompile blur in debug
  * cc0792c1 hyprland-uwsm.desktop: Add TryExec
  * 28c9122a [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * 55076eda versionkeeper: don't pop up on initial launch
  * 81cd526f cursor: fix screencopy cursor pos and duplicate shape with
    sw cursors (#10519)
  * bd4733a0 flake.lock: update
  * 4f161da3 hyprpm: ignore pins when adding a package with a git rev
    (#10502)
  * 185c9684 input: unhide cursor on tablet events after touch events
    (#10484)
  * b90910c0 renderer: add wrapping options to renderTexture method
    (#10497)
  * eb3b38d4 eventLoop: fixup event source callbacks
  * d9c8a378 input: always allow focus to permission popups
  * 158c0f29 permissions: add permission management for keyboards
    (#10367)
  * 44cb8f76 internal: added error log when getEdgeDefinedPoint is
    impossible (#10462)
  * 705b97c4 input: revert #10416 and #10418
  * c19f3836 hyprpm: fix crash with enable without an arg
  * bb5cd5b2 screencopy: store a fb before permission popup if the
    permission is pending (#10455)
  * bb9aa79b hyprpm: reject remove without a param
  * dfa48362 hyprpm: fix execute permission bit on installed dirs
    (#10435)
  * 18377d22 [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * 2aa21625 input: ensure seat grabs from exclusive layers can be
    dismissed (#10418)
  * 29460090 input: do not send mouse events when outside of a surface
    (#10416)
  * b0cc4921 protocols: simulate mouse movement after activating a
    toplevel (#10429)
  * a5c9b3e4 core: Include cstring whenever strncpy is used (#10404)
  * dfb841c3 desktop: prevent layers from dismissing their own seat
    grabs on map (#10417)
  * 5ceb0ec1 core: drop the legacy renderer (#10408)
  * f707d869 protocols/hyprland-surface: account for scaled monitor
    positions (#10415)
  * 75f2cb5f xwayland: do not include xcb.h when xwayland is disabled
    (#10407)
  * a51e639d input: disallow virtual keyboards from changing LED state
    (#10402)
  * 59b23406 opengl: add missing vao for screenshader (#10397)
  * da3583fd opengl: publicize shader creation/usage functions (#10378)
  * 04124988 opengl: optimize shaders and reduce unneeded drawcalls
    (#10364)
  * 390a3578 renderer: use alpha for the lockttytext texture
  * 9a87498b renderer: minor damage fixes
  * f58bb72d renderer: render blur on fade out (#10356)
  * 60cd5b7a renderer: always render snapshots as 8bit
  * 25cf06f6 build: require hyprgraphics>=0.1.3 (#10350)
  * e44aae0c hyprpm: switch to numeric owner/group after f8bbe5124c00
    (#10345)
  * fcb6f936 hyprpm: add missing include for libc++ after 1c530cbc66db
    (#10344)

