hyprland (0.49.0-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.49.0
  * 9958d297 version: bump to 0.49.0
  * 239cdd67 socket2: fix order of window events on map (#10341)
  * f01e3043 desktop: cleanup code and use std::ranges (#10289)
  * 04c98abd layout: properly assign workspace and monitor when moving a
    child to the parent (#10338)
  * 53bfb92d layout: allow interacting with pinned windows when
    fullscreened (#10326)
  * 2b3cac01 flake.lock: update
  * f909b0f1 opengl: fix legacyrenderer
