hyprland (0.48.0-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.48.0
  * 5ee35f91 version: bump to 0.48.0
  * aa1bd647 core/Compositor.hpp: fix non-relative Texture import
    (#9703)
  * fdb7ca6c core/compositor: Fix dropping cursor buffer data early
    (#9700)
  * 6ab5a0be renderer: fix cm_fs_passthrough (#9698)
  * 6384f4ac core/compositor: Correctly track SHM buffer damage (#9678)
  * 4600043a hyprpm: return 1 when plugins are outdated (#9694)
  * 279b0604 screencopy, render: Use explicit sync for screencopy
    (#9697)
  * ccbdba7e syncobj: refactor point timelines (#9689)
  * c7f0519f core: fix DS and VRR automation (#9334)
  * 7ea4fbf0 types: Upgrade buffer ref from WP to SP (#9677)
  * f6ca4bac syncobj: restore SHM buffer reset (#9675)
  * 155eba57 groupbar: remove 2 pixel gap above groupbar (#9664)
  * 7b10530a XWayland: restore the abstract socket, and make it optional
    (#9615)
  * a25a2145 dmabuf: pop buffer on failure (#9620)
  * c8d80a29 ci: Fail on warnings (#9668)
  * 03385fc0 seatmgr: avoid crash on null surfs
  * cca0f48b renderer: add an option to disable cm and auto-skip cm if
    not necessary
  * 60edb376 config/defaultConfig.hpp: windowrulev2 -> windowrule
    (#9663)
  * 6f74d8d7 example/hyprland.conf: windowrulev2 -> windowrule (#9662)
  * ec4bea79 config: nuke windowrule v1 syntax
  * 9171db19 renderer: delete now redundant ifdefs (#9651)
  * 5f60fc7d renderer: only commit hw cursor stuff if needed (#9654)
  * c4f46473 monitor: Optimize direct scanout damage (#9653)
  * 011d7ccb internal: Fix compiler warnings (#9646)
  * efc51eb7 managers: Use primary backend for cursor swapchain (#9645)
  * c2835b6b groupbar: remove recursive window recalc (#9561)
  * d5d7f69d flake.lock: update
  * 5cef2f44 renderer: allow commits when buffer is unchanged but cursor
    changed (#9648)
  * 22154fa2 opengl: simplify cm pipeline
  * 2ddd16ef CMake: install frag files (for real this time)
  * d7382aa8 CMake: install frag files
  * 90306bda Meson: include frags in globber
  * b1ab0f75 splashes: update for 3ya
  * bf5e4bf1 syncobj: dont crash compositor on protocol errors (#9627)
  * 4c471218 renderer: fix window offset for dragged windows (#9629)
  * e5968048 input: Fix clicking through groupbar tabs (#9606)
  * f4315db5 nix: mesa -> libgbm (#9612)
  * 3cc8e8c6 renderer: don't crash if cm fails to compile
  * b3794460 protocols: fix include
  * f4995c18 descriptions: remove allow_early_buffer_release
  * 6ffde364 syncobj: use eventfd instead of stalling fd checks (#9437)
  * c754d796  nix: remove wayland-protocols overlay and bump flake
    (#9613)
  * 8c97cb78 renderer: add simple color management (#9506)
  * e86d3a14 groupbar: add an option to adjust gap sizes (#9578)
  * 4b25fbe5 windows: respect noinitialfocus with workspace changes
    (#9586)
  * 81e93acb groupbar: pass alpha to title tex render pass
  * b21edb1a input: fix touch calibration matrix overriding
  * e4af4b5e core: update decorations on lockgroups (#9573)
  * d30cc19d renderer: skip ds commits if buffer didn't change (#9556)
  * f15b49e0 core: prevent crash when monitor list is empty (#9572)
  * c544c511 windowrules: store floating size on close instead of resize
    (#9569)
  * b80b64cd windowrules: add option to allow size persistence between
    app launches (#9422)
  * 4082e876 [gha] Nix: update inputs
  * 8ce1665f protocols: Fix blocked color management get_information
    (#9563)
  * 7753e8ea keybinds): prevent crash when executing movewindoworgroup
    (#9551)
  * cb4230e1 touch: reject swipe on locked sessions
  * 7055d0c1 master: add option to keep master window position (#9537)
  * 4435f5c5 input: fixup mouse check for flipping x / y (#9529)
  * 7a84317f protocols: Fix cursor shape protocol valid shape check
    (#9547)
  * 24337607 hyprctl: Error handling improvements, minor cleanups
    (#9536)
  * b51ab182 socket2: add activespecialv2 (#9530)
  * d7e7a292 input: add flip_x and flip_y for touchpad (#9481)
  * f1ef724a protocols: Ensure protocol dtors are called in
    ProtocolManager dtor (#9521)
  * 474bfcbc core: fix clang-format
  * 905ca39b nix/module: toHyprconf -> toHyprlang (#9221)
  * 3a21dd84 core: cleanup some smart pointer usage
  * e6be4af2 core: add default initializers for ccompositor ptrs
  * 2c78867a core: cleanup window properties
  * 2acbb59b core: ignore internal move workspace calls if the workspace
    doesn't change (#9516)
  * 11943f76 monitor: avoid crash on expired special workspace monitor
    owner
  * f148b96b input: Provide a non-zero time for button release triggered
    during window unmap. (#9513)
  * 445337d0 protocols: Fix IWaylandProtocol onDisplayDestroy m_pGlobal
    double-free (#9507)
  * 34f2a471 core: Add null activeWorkspace check in
    moveWorkspaceToMonitor (#9503)
  * d5920bc5 internal: fix include paths (#9500)
  * aee9b8ac protocols: fix relative include
  * 32a3d84d protocols: fix wrong iface for xdg_dialog
  * 002cd91f nix: wp-protocol version bump (#9494)
  * 01f40744 hyprctl/layers: print pid for layershell clients (#9468)
  * 6787fe89 protocols: Support wp color management proto (#9444)
  * f0850905 cmake: add CXX_STANDARD_REQUIRED flag to ensure c++ version
    must be c++26 (#9476)
  * d1ea18b4 hyprctl/config: fixup config descriptions, fill out missing
    ones, provide more data
  * 73ae9790 hyprpm: add --hl-url for custom forks
  * 3458d7ac xwayland: improve dnd and cleanup (#9405)
  * e5946462 config: fix a possible crash in the monitor config parser
    (#9460)
  * 2e816489 internal: use isNumber from hyprutils (#9467)
  * 8f50460b xcursor: move config check to sync gsettings (#9473)
  * f4b148df anr: add xwayland support (#9456)
  * 0e24f9c0 anr: add a note for no pid dialogs
  * 2cfa5d24 hyprctl: Add IPC support for Hyprsunset (#9315)
  * fa246cb6 flake.lock: update hyprutils and aquamarine
  * 6d25ef09 xwayland: add INCR support for clipboard transfers (#9434)
  * 0137a5f6 anr: capitalize options
  * 3c1a2e9f config/descriptions: add enable_anr_dialog
  * fb8eaba8 core: add an ANR dialog
  * 3352317c scripts/generateVersion.sh: convert to posix (#9433)
  * e59623d1 hyprctl: don't return empty str if there are no global
    shortcuts
  * d01f9943 subsurfaces: dont try to access popup surfaces when
    handling subsurface updates (#9421)
  * 59c615c3 input: add follow_mouse_threshold (#9392)
  * e2a92711 animations: add the gnomed animation style for windows
  * 897ee276 xwayland: configure on a configure request and cleanup
    geometry conversion (#9375)
  * 94a30889 keybinds: fix some errors not returning a failure (#9416)
  * 9228116c xwayland: fix a possible clipboard race condition (#9394)
  * 410da2e4 workspaces: update persistence on workspace rename (#9368)
  * 7a6fde84 internal: redirect exec'd app output to /dev/null (#9411)
  * 3eb6cb18 syncobj: ensure we only add waiters on succesful checks
    (#9412)
  * 2f967037 config: set no_hw_cursors to auto by default and disable on
    tearing
  * 1309b59f monitor: report a scheduled frame when tearing on cursor
    move
  * fb36815b renderer: remove spammy log
  * df3fba15 internal: remove unused variable (#9402)
  * 40adb3df config: actually set initial beziers (#9400)
  * 5d2b0082 renderer: disable explicit if aquamarine output doesn't
    support it (#9396) (#9398)
  * 208f94fe animations: sync inactive/active border angles when using
    borderangle animations (#9401)
  * 17894051 session-lock: send locked when in unsafe state (#9399)
  * 68bb3e7f env: move XDG_SESSION_TYPE to before backend init (#9390)
  * f83fe998 protocols: add version 2 of ext-idle-notify-v1 protocol
    (#8959)
  * f2d43e5f nix/overlays: add wayland-protocols overlay
  * e1179b66 flake.lock: update
  * f261fb6f groupbar: fix groupbar missing when indicator_height is <=
    0
  * 3a43e7bb config: default movefocus_cycles_fullscreen to false
  * 1f97643e core: add mallopt to modify trim threshold
  * 56f6f615 tablet: take `active_area_size` into account when sending
    tip event (#9325)
  * 8e10ddb5 datadevice: fix wrong param (#9370)
  * feb8ad48 groups: deactivate unfocused windows in groups (#9354)
  * f7fcbe32 renderer: various fixes towards improving gpu calls
    robustness (#9188)
  * a724332e desktop: add ability to target pinned windows in workspace
    rules (#9344)
  * 54441e0c renderer: fix fade out on silent moves to special
  * acbcf0cf toplevelexport: fix transformed origin for shm buffers
    (#9343)
  * 30b49c75 popup: improve ::at() behavior
  * ff9e059d window: move size reporting to animation begin callback
    (#9298)
  * f1e32cd1 core: avoid .at() and use [] operator (#9347)
  * 868b2b54 window: fix missing surface null checks to prevent crashes
    (#9350)
  * 8a6778f0 scripts: don't overwrite generated version if we're not in
    a git repo
  * 64591c85 nix: add hydraJobs output for aggregating Hyprland build
    jobs
  * 873bff39 renderer: fix missing null checks to prevent crashes
    (#9332)
  * 84c9baec keybinds: Added `toggleswallow` dispatcher (#5548)
  * 3b99e906 compositor: don't iterate over unmapped ls-es in vectorToLS
  * 5e729243 compositor: guard null ws in updating fade
  * 70cfc7cc cmonitor: guard old workspace
  * 1da0b2c0 subprojects: update h-p
  * 708d1663 dispatchers: add cyclenext hist option (#9055)
  * 44004abc config: fix includes
  * 31431a92 protocols: Support content-type-v1 proto (#9226)
  * 70d94fec refactor: clang-tidy in compositor (#9241)
  * 37310810 protocols: implement hyprland-ctm-control rev 2 (#9267)
  * 97a24ec6 Nix: change meson buildtype from debugoptimized to debug
  * 64fefa37 desktop: move popups to UPs and fix missing subsurface
    resource
  * e380b6ed popup: take xdg geometry into account in input calcs
  * 88adae73 pass: add input region debug
  * c6f67225 desktop: move popup and subsurface ctors to factories
  * 5b43c106 animation: don't immediately disconnect active vars during
    tick (#9272)
  * d11d0697 CI/Nix: remove deprecated magic-nix-cache-action
  * ddf180fa render: enforce framebuffer offloading and remove
    introspection toggle (#9217)
  * a4b7d1c2 xwayland: correct pointer coordinate mismatch in X11
    windows (#9259)
  * 12b5034c configWatcher: watch both symlinks and canonical paths
    (#9219)
  * 9c382874 groupbar: various visual improvements
  * ac566819 desktop: fix segfault when destroying a partially create
    layer surface (#9247)
  * 7d51dee1 hyprctl: Extract IPC code to separate method (#9223)
  * ea16b64e xwayland: prevent invalid window configurations for X11
    apps (#9253)
  * e6a9cfab monitor: preferred mode now tries first 3 modes if
    preferred fails before erroring (#9246)
  * ef03f691 xwayland: handle window coords correctly (#9238)
  * 32c0fa2f core: begin using CFileDescriptor from hyprutils (#9122)
  * 7d1c78f4 core,hyprctl: clang, clang-tidy, typo fixes and dtors
    changes (#9233)
  * d462cc7f subsurface: fix invalid parent typo
  * 09ec1cca popup: stop refocusing at unmap
  * 6fc9c8e4 flake.lock: update
  * 61319197 monitor: round refresh rates in sorting modes
  * aaa5573c config/hyprctl: fix keyword not updating autoreload
  * 344e32d7 pass/rect: fix bounding / opaque regions
  * d41135d0 input: change window grab cursor to closed hand (#9196)
  * b884f1f7 renderer: calculate UV using both pixel and monitor
    dimensions (#9210)
  * 3d1dd6b5 presentation: log a fixme when there is a feedback leak
  * 1d3904c3 configmgr: properly free glob memory
  * 529ad4ea ikeyboard: free xkbSymState in clearManuallyAllocd
  * d3042e53 xwayland: respect window size set by configure requests
    (#9190)
  * d2773d7a deps: add libinotify-kqueue on BSDs after 8dd2cd41fb4c
    (#9197)
  * 5fd90548 nix: fix duplicate inputs and update flake.lock
  * 25d5ce48 CI/setup_base: add libspng
  * e7a72de9 xwayland: send synthetic configure events (#9193)
  * cb7ed4f6 ci: clang-format fix (#9145)
  * 2a478c30 core: fix clang-format

