hyprland (0.47.0-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.47.0
  * 04ac46c5 version: bump to 0.47.0
  * 2f55806d renderer: fix rare case when a tiled window would be
    rendered over fs
  * 3b207d29 core: update groups on movewindow (#9183)
  * 6bd6c551 hooksystem: avoid huge include for HANDLE
  * bb5b09de renderer: fix funky corners
  * efe29a24 shadow: avoid drawing empty shadows
  * e9510115 renderer/internal: stop using box pointers
  * 16aeb24b core: make persistent workspaces always follow the config
  * 74d0f34c pointer: always scale the cpu cursor to the right size
  * 4abf9155 window: only set m_iMonitorMovedFrom when the workspace is
    visible (#9178)
  * 0a28e137 desktop: move desktop types to memory-safe pointers
  * 3cd6e396 xwayland: fix pointer mismatches with multiple monitors
    (#9179)
  * 8b1d6e30 subsurface: damage the entire parent on size change
  * 445acec2 core: move sendWindowSize off of xwaylandmgr
  * 45c3787e window: revert only set m_iMonitorMovedFrom, when moving to
    a different monitor
  * 9199a974 input: pass touch events to lock screens (#9129)
  * bce58d9d dwindle: fix possible crash on null ws
  * f3fc8d59 config/ConfigWatcher.cpp: add missing include needed for
    clang (#9166)
  * 107723bd config: disable borderangle by default (#9165)
  * 065e8964 flake.lock: update
  * 354d4594 xwayland: various window handling fixes
  * 089fdd1e window: only set m_iMonitorMovedFrom, when moving to a
    different monitor (#9160)
  * 1815f9a2 compositor: fix incorrect cast, use lambda capture instead
    (#9161)
  * d8f79d76 core: add --verify-config to verify the config with
    Hyprland
  * 80b2fd13 animations: fix borderangle once (#9149)
  * fda9790c layout: force full damage on toggling floating mode
  * 9b3f7139 layershell: check if layer is valid (#9156)
  * 0e5d03a5 datadevice: do the unfocus surface stuff before dndActive
    is true (#9157)
  * 57a39984 input: abord dnd op on escape pressed
  * 944e36ea config: fix misc:disable_autoreload
  * 4a1b960c layout: set window size after toggling floating
  * 5d8261ae xwayland: avoid sending value of real size to xwayland
  * d075d1ca pass/rect: fix bounding box
  * bb099e57 pass/rect: fix box shrinking with bb
  * dadb2e09 opengl: use uv to avoid rendering the entire blurbox
  * a8c2d5a6 layout: damage window properly on float mode changes
  * 465cf66d protocols: add hyprland_surface_v1.set_visible_region
    implementation (#9120)
  * 1a0a22ad configmgr: fix crash on very early plugin loads
  * 0a1ae48a core: move all shared_ptrs from the STL to hyprutils
    (#9143)
  * ae403e6a flake.lock: update
  * ae4e38d9 tablet: send `motion`s on tip events (#9132)
  * ecae3c5e ci: fix "Resource not accessible by integration" for cf
    workflow (#9144)
  * f1bd6280 core/renderer: Add GPU hotplug support (#8980)
  * fda56265 xwayland: fix sending large clipboard data (#9134)
  * c90dbfab xwayland: fix clipboard mime name and atom mismatch (#9137)
  * d335c8f1 fractional-scale: avoid redundant and duplicate scale
    events
  * c8a0443a config/ConfigManager.cpp: add instruction to edit config
    (#9130)
  * ce48bc54 flake.lock: update (#9128)
  * da6e9663 keybinds: add visible arg for cyclenext (#9045)
  * a661203b xwayland: fix crash when trying to initialize without
    Xwayland installed (#9077)
  * 9e8d9791 xwayland: support sending clipboard change notification on
    focus (#9111)
  * 2d82a923 config: fix float animation speeds < 0 (#9123)
  * 40745316 protocols: add hyprland_lock_notify_v1 implementation
    (#9092)
  * 8dd2cd41 core: move to inotify for monitoring the config files
  * 0a0e56d9 core: use readFileAsString instead of cat for os-release
  * 086fd7ec protocols: do not destroy screencopy resources before
