  * 2778aff0 animations: fix XWayland cursor glitch and refactor skill
    issues (#9033)
  * 9e4f90ae animation: fixup adding animvars during ::tick (#9030)
  * 15dc024a keybinds: fix previous_per_monitor logic (#9010)
  * 3b85690a config: add exec(-onec) with rules and execr(-once) (#8953)
  * cef09fbf animation: avoid crashes in ::tick() on mutations
  * a8b568c6 core: Add render:allow_early_buffer_release to make buffer
    release configurable (#9019)
  * b5fb6110 core: Add a periodic donation request (#8981)
  * da9252a2 keybinds: fix nullptr deref in forcekillactive (#9021)
  * 8475a8ef core: always use goal size to send to clients
  * f9c37ca4 windows: honor xdg_toplevel_set_fullscreen output hint
    (#8965)
  * 9dc9366f config: fix animations requiring all args
  * 85aba23c ci(clang-format): directly do the clang-format instead of
