  * 2d1ebadb selectors: add a tag: to for matching window tag(s) by
    regex (#8985)
  * e66eab7b animationmgr: don't warp based on POINTY value (#9000)
  * c9822b08 keybinds: add new window destruction dispatchers (#8962)
  * 983bc067 opengl: fix crash on null fb stencil op
  * b320bc2d core: use cpu-buffer hw cursors on nvidia by default
  * ad64726f opengl: only allocate offMainFB on demand
  * 5fa25946 renderer: don't access hdrMetadata optional if it has no
    value (#8987)
  * 75727e7c protocols: fix compilation error (#8988)
  * 67e1e46f window: fixup fade out animation on silent moves
  * 308b1f3a core: minor fixes for animation rewrite
  * c1439078 config: update animation even if disabled
  * 830350a1 core: Add support for HDR and color management protocols
    (#8715)
