  * fd67ee9e layout: apply group rules after window creation (#8779)
  * bec18dc6 core: fix possible crash on null active workspace
  * 5b714f05 internal: Make static analysis more happy (#8767)
  * 7c43eed2 hyprpm: fix hyrpm sometimes returning 0 despite errors
