hyprland (0.46.2-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.46.2
  * 0bd541f2 version: bump to 0.46.2
  * 23d00cdd layout: apply group rules after window creation (#8779)
  * 061241d3 core: fix possible crash on null active workspace
  * b9df70be hyprpm: fix hyrpm sometimes returning 0 despite errors
    occuring (#8761)
  * 9583429e core: Unbreak build on FreeBSD (#8762)
  * 747c3811 xwayland: fix compile with no xwayland
  * 508e8234 xwm: fixup targets in selection requests
  * ec0a3830 xwayland: fix dnd including xwayland
  * d0bffc4f core: avoid activating toplevel-less surfaces
  * 07a19e2c hyprctl: Fix `hyprctl` batch JSON command (#8749)
  * 46d5b363 windowrules: fixup duplicate rule enum tags

