hyprland (0.46.0-1ppa1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Update to release 0.46.0
  * 788ae588 version: bump to 0.46.0
  * bba2d9a1 versionkeeper: init version to 0.0.0 if no file is present
  * e340e9f4 nix/meson: add re2 dependency (#8738)
  * c2d14a20 opengl: fixup missed /4 in oklab parsing
  * 95cdedee windowrules: fix prop rules with boolean values
  * 0706c1a1 layerrules: fix ignorezero not working
  * aecf1abd opengl: fixup invalid ogl uniform reads
  * b9f82e99 animationmgr: fixup stack-use-after-return
  * e06b5204 core: Move regex from stdlib to re2 (#8736)
  * dab50b3e core: Optimize window/layer rule application and scanning
    (#8735)
  * eaac5c7c flake.lock: update
  * a5234f26 core: drop using deques in favor of vectors
  * de3ad245 input: add warp_back_after_non_mouse_input
